textToTaxIDs(String) - Method in class gnat.filter.ner.AliBabaSpeciesNer
Deprecated. Takes a text and returns a set of species that are discussed therein.
Alternatively, if the PubMed ID of a text is known and only the abstract is needed, run AliBabaSpeciesNer.pmidToTaxIDs(int) to get taxon IDs and potentially use cached results.
Use #textToTaxIDsAndNames(String) is you need species IDs and the mentions used to refer to them in the text.
